(79, 2, '2019-09-18 15:42:41', '2019-09-18 14:42:41', 'We tried to name our sexy little dive bar after our idol but he turned us down and instead got all of our online shit deleted. Now we stand alone as cease &amp; desist. We stand for the freedom to do what you want and the challenge of conventions. We welcome all in our bar and do not discriminate. That being said, hen parties can fuck right off. We are stupid, we have fun and we don’t give a fuck about what people think. Greasy food ‘till late, bangin’ drinks ‘till even later and having a god damn laugh is all we care about.', 'Cease & Desist', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cease-desist', '', '', '2019-09-18 15:44:49', '2019-09-18 14:44:49', '', 0, 'https://brightonwc.wpengine.com/?post_type=venue&#038;p=79', 0, 'venue', '', 0),
